{"tid":1721674,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Poly唔撚洗幫 走啦","createTime":"2019-11-14T17:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T02:24:58.000Z","uid":259164,"like":9,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"368dc6cf8a4644c6248458abc66dcdb04f028f7a","tid":1721674,"uid":259164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T17:12:21.000Z","msg":"今朝入去幫手 一直風平浪靜，夜晚休息坐低個時有手足彈句:唔係poly既人就走。過多一陣突然poly正門有個fullgear既手足行岀黎，話佢頭先係poly入面比poly既手足打左一拳 話佢唔係poly既學生。我地成班聽到真係好撚燥。其他人又話聽到話有人話fa呃飯食。最撚搞笑係8點左右係物質站有人話有狗入左去，唔撚比人再入物資站，搞撚到啲前線水都冇得飲。入去問啲poly學生，佢地話朝早開始已經聽到有人搞分化。亦都話遲啲會岀聲明。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，cu發夢，個撚個幾撚團結。垃圾poly。"},{"pid":"688317dddd0303eb4c3b333ef811048d34f1b49c","tid":1721674,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T17:12:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">入去retweet like reply</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Twitter吹大雞！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">！！！McConnell支持法案，重點推 </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senatemajldr/status/1195006159679299584\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatemajldr%2Fstatus%2F1195006159679299584&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc66VNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=5f4f88b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatemajldr%2Fstatus%2F1195006159679299584&h=8c1d25b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/senatemajldr/status/1195006159679299584</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Rick 多謝 McConnell <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1195011922799804416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1195011922799804416&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc66VNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=8d9e9a29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1195011922799804416&h=d2960883\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/119